### Privacy Flags

- `enable_pii_detection` and `enable_pii_redaction` control detection/masking; RL `strict` arm forces both on.
- Pass per-call overrides via `context` when needed.

### Retention

- Respect `max_retention_days_by_ns` from `config/policy.yaml`.
- Sweeper deletes outdated provenance entries; support dry runs.
